text: Cochea is a corregimiento in David District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 2,447 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,790; its population as of 2000 was 2,004. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
